what_worked: Applied date_cte_isolate: Extracted the shared date filter into a single CTE (`filtered_dates`) and pushed it into each channel's UNION branches, converting implicit joins to explicit JOIN syntax. This avoids redundant scans of `date_dim` and allows early filtering of fact tables.
why_it_worked: Pre-filtering date dimension into CTE reduces hash join probe table from 73K to ~365 rows
